dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Depths shown by soundings. Includes 2 ancillary maps: Site of Jerusalem -- Suez Bay. Includes 17 photographic views of the Holy Land by James Graham. In lower right-hand corner: Photographic views by Graham.
